item.title: 【HD Live Performances】HDTV - Carly Rae Jepsen - Primavera Sound Sao Paulo Festival, Brazil, 03-12-2023
item.description:
I made another version based on ilya2129's recording (credits to that user): I moved the video and 2 audio tracks (I skipped the third one since it was the same as the second one) into a MKV container (no quality loss), I added chapters with each song and I added an info file with the setlist.



Setlist:
1. Let's Sort the Whole Thing Out
2. Run Away With Me
3. Talking to Yourself
4. Shy Boy
5. Kollage
6. Psychedelic Switch
7. Call Me Maybe
8. I Really Like You
9. Want You in My Room
10. The Loneliest Time
11. Go Find Yourself or Whatever
12. Cut to the Feeling
